{"word":"αὐθεντέω","slug":"αὐθεντέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>αὐϑεντέω</el></b> [<el>αὐϑέντης</el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gener.\">gener.</a> = ‘one who takes matters into one’s own hands’] ‘function in a directive manner’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><i>exercise authority over,</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διδάσκω\">διδάσκω</a></el> in effect = <i>tell a man what to do</i> <b><a href='B:610 2:12'>1 Ti 2:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:αὐθαίρετος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:αὐλέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}